short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: A 'Smaller. Smarter.' way to navigate txwes.edu

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This is an alumni created chrome extension to quickly access Texas Wesleyan University online resources.

Select your user type and get quick links to Texas Wesleyan's major online services or search the site. Feel free to contact the developer for suggestions, improvements and bugs.
